Subject: Secret money control in Spain
Message-ID: <1994Jul22.183642.2329@goofy.fi.upm.es>
From: mgallar@asterix.fi.upm.es (Miguel Angel Gallardo Ortiz)
Date: 22 Jul 94 18:36:42 +0200
